---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="页面未找到"
  description="您访问的页面不存在"
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-20 md:py-32 text-center">
    <p class="text-8xl md:text-9xl font-display font-bold text-accent-200">404</p>
    <h1 class="mt-6 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-semibold text-accent-900">页面未找到</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-accent-500">您访问的页面不存在或已被移除。不妨从首页开始浏览。</p>
    <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/" class="btn-primary">返回首页</a>
      <a href="/spaces" class="btn-outline">浏览案例</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
